setting.activity: This recording takes place at the family's home, at Montigny-Aux-Amognes, and more precisely in the bathroom and in the child's bedroom. The father is giving the child her bath. Then, the child prepares the toys that she wants to take with her on holidays. After that, the child playsrole-playing games with her mother, the waitress and the cook.
